====================================================
General
====================================================

1. /presentation/general/messages/0
mock data
Route: /messages
Shared page for all staff roles.
Highlights:
- Thread list with job context and unread state.
- Main conversation area with job-linked messages and audit trail value.
Section description: Shows how internal communication works across every role without repeating the page inside each role deck.

2. /presentation/general/newsfeed/1
mock data
Route: /newsfeed
Shared page for all staff roles.
Highlights:
- Internal updates and company announcements.
- Staff-wide information area that replaces buried email reminders.
Section description: Shows the shared staff newsfeed once inside the General deck instead of repeating it for every role.

3. /presentation/general/profile/2
mock data
Route: /profile
Profile work tab.
Highlights:
- Work and Personal tab switcher.
- Work KPI card group for hours, payslips, estimated pay, and leave.
- Work summary sections for leave, emergency contact, attendance, overtime, and staff vehicles.
Section description: Shows the staff work profile as a self-service area for employment, HR, clocking, payslip, and staff record information.

4. /presentation/general/profile-tab-personal/3
mock data
Route: /profile?tab=personal
Profile personal tab.
Highlights:
- Work and Personal tab switcher.
- Personal dashboard insights.
- Personal widget grid and configurable private dashboard areas.
Section description: Shows the personal profile area separately from work data, with private planning widgets and personal dashboard sections.

5. /presentation/general/login/4
mock data
Route: /login
Shared login page.
Highlights:
- Staff/customer login card.
- Password reset entry point.
- Dev login section hidden inside /presentation.
Section description: Shows the real login presentation view without exposing the development login selector during demos.


